'config' file goes in ~/.config/<here>
'light_bg' and 'dark_bg' should be placed in ~/.config/<here> for cleanliness:
    ensure they are called correctly by .Xresources

when making changes to .Xresources, run this to load them:
xrdb -merge .Xresources

urxvt
copy->paste
highlight selection like a normal human being, (right click can be used to extend it), 
  in the desired area, press "ctrl + insert" to paste
